*Ostrvu* je nedavno posetila kraljica. (The island was recently visited by the queen.)

Bio je jedan čovek koji je često putovao na razne *ostrve*. (There was a man who often traveled to various islands.)

Udaljenost između dva *ostrva* je bila ogromna. (The distance between two islands was huge.)

Naša deca su obožavala da igraju na *ostrvu*. (Our children loved to play on the island.)

Mnogi su se odselili sa *ostrva*. (Many people moved away from the island.)